{"tid":1679590,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(天滅中共系列) 解放軍3名曾參與國慶閱兵機師身亡","createTime":"2019-10-28T09:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T09:59:39.000Z","uid":233643,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9a1e3c699eb1d2f32c598e985aaab73b51164168","tid":1679590,"uid":233643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:39:45.000Z","msg":"解放軍3名機師在訓練期間墜機身亡，全部曾參與國慶閱兵。根據內地傳媒報道，解放軍本月11日在河南新野進行飛行訓練時，飛機出現故障，機師為了村民安全並無降落在山上，結果撞向山崖墜機，33歲機師和機上2人都身亡。3人在意外前個多星期的十一國慶閱兵，參加了組成「70」圖案的飛行表演。<br />\n<br />\n三名殉職機師分別是:<br />\n<br />\n溫偉彬，男，湖南桃江人，1982年10月出生，中共黨員，解放軍某部飛行員，二級空中機械師。  <br />\n<br />\n龔大川，男，河南新野人，1986年6月出生，中共黨員，解放軍某部一級飛行員。<br />\n<br />\n羅偉，男，四川瀘州人，1995年1月出生，中共黨員，解放軍某部三級飛行員，二級副駕駛。"},{"pid":"83270ebc834dba9fb71f069d66fed2379d005769","tid":1679590,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:39:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Mfv693.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Mfv693.jpg&h=975a7fc9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c8756eeb2d079a22d8a70aa26692ccc4584c2465","tid":1679590,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:40:49.000Z","msg":"熱烈地彈琴熱烈地唱"},{"pid":"ce16f96f824fd2942ae2a1fbc260fe70bd13cf9d","tid":1679590,"uid":272976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:41:18.000Z","msg":"不能為之非不為之<br />\n又白事當紅事，祝你多啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e0084b23097297ed6d5a03e6bd1d76d2e52eec","tid":1679590,"uid":233643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce16f96f824fd2942ae2a1fbc260fe70bd13cf9d","tid":1679590,"uid":272976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:41:18.000Z","msg":"不能為之非不為之<br />\n又白事當紅事，祝你多啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:42:19.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦傻鳩五毛共狗<br />\n祝你快手死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoh